## Description
Add UI in the setup wizard for monitoring and optionally conducting the bootstrap conversation directly in the browser.

## UI Components

### Bootstrap Progress Panel
- Shows in wizard step 7 when bootstrap is active
- Displays: current section name, completed sections / total sections, progress bar
- Real-time updates via PubSub from BootstrapSession

### Embedded Chat (optional)
- Simple chat interface for conducting bootstrap directly in LiveView
- Input box, message history, send button
- Messages routed through the workspace main agent with bootstrap prompt
- Shows agent questions and user responses

### Post-Bootstrap File Viewer
- After bootstrap completes, show generated files
- Read-only markdown preview of each file
- Edit button to modify files (creates new revision)
- Regenerate option to re-run bootstrap

### Continue Elsewhere Prompt
- If user has Telegram connected, show Continue on Telegram button
- Shows QR code or deep link to Telegram chat
- Progress still visible in LiveView via PubSub

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Progress panel shows real-time bootstrap progress
- [ ] Embedded chat works for conducting bootstrap in browser
- [ ] Generated files viewable after completion
- [ ] Continue on Telegram option when Telegram connected
- [ ] PubSub-driven real-time updates
- [ ] Graceful handling of bootstrap timeout/failure
- [ ] LiveView tests for progress display